OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FWe just learned that the world's most
OL,7,Fpowerful person, Donald Trump, has a
OL,8,Fboss: the bond market.
OL,10,FHe may not have acknowledged this to
OL,11,Fhimself, yet, but the global financial
OL,12,Ftumult he caused - and has temporarily
OL,13,Feased - has locked him in a fiscal
OL,14,Fprison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
