OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FBecause, as I have been saying for 24
OL,7,Fhours, he came perilously close on
OL,8,FWednesday to having caused such an
OL,9,Fextreme fall in the price of US
OL,10,Fgovernment debt that it would have
OL,11,Fbecome prohibitively expensive for his
OL,12,Fadministration to fund a large deficit
OL,13,F- more than 6% of GDP - and also to
OL,14,Frefinance the almost $8 trillion of
OL,15,Fgovernment debt that matures in the
OL,16,Fcoming year (almost a third of
OL,17,FAmerica's sovereign debt).
OL,19,FThe point is he is totally dependent
OL,20,Fon the goodwill of bond investors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
