OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FAnd when he announced his reckless
OL,7,Froster of massive tariffs eight days
OL,8,Fago he alienated them, because they
OL,9,Ffeared he would tank the economy such
OL,10,Fthat tax revenues would plummet and
OL,11,Fthe deficit would balloon.
OL,13,FSo they sold US government bonds,
OL,14,FTreasuries, and the yield on the bonds
OL,15,F- the de facto interest rate - soared.
OL,17,FWhich is why Trump blinked, and put on
OL,18,Fhold the more extreme tariffs, except
OL,19,Ffor the 145% on China, for 90 days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
