OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FYou might think the worst part of this
OL,7,Fis the uncertainty he has created for
OL,8,Fbusinesses and investors for the next
OL,9,F90 days. Since no one in their right
OL,10,Fmind would make a major US investment
OL,11,Funtil the final tariff determinations
OL,12,Fare made.
OL,14,FBut the cancerous uncertainty is not
OL,15,Fthe worst of it.
OL,17,FThe worst of it is he has shredded any
OL,18,Frespect that overseas governments and
OL,19,Finvestors might have had for America's
OL,20,Feconomic and fiscal competence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
