OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FAll of which means that bond and stock
OL,7,Fmarkets will remain fragile and
OL,8,Fvolatile - fearful that Trump will
OL,9,Fregain his mojo and engage in some
OL,10,Fother fiscal extravagance.
OL,12,FHe has also handed a loaded gun to his
OL,13,Fperceived enemy, China, and his
OL,14,Fsupposed ally Japan.
OL,16,FThis matters in both cases, because he
OL,17,Fis engaged in the mother of all trade
OL,18,Fwars with China - and Japan wants a
OL,19,Ftrade deal with him that would see it
OL,20,Fescape mega tariffs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
