OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FThe loaded guns they have are their
OL,7,Fmassive loans to the US government.
OL,8,FJapan owns more than a trillion
OL,9,Fdollars of US Treasuries and China not
OL,10,Fmuch less.
OL,12,FIf they were to sell those bonds, or
OL,13,Feven if they chose not to refinance
OL,14,Fmaturing bonds, that could be a
OL,15,Fdisaster for Trump. Because it could
OL,16,Fcause another potentially crippling
OL,17,Fspike in bond yields.
OL,19,FHere is the measure of Trump's debacle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
