OL,3,CHow Trump just shackled himself in a
OL,4,Cfiscal prison
OL,6,FHe may well have trashed America's
OL,7,Fsingle most important financial
OL,8,Fcompetitive advantage, namely that
OL,9,Finvestors have traditionally bought
OL,10,Fthe dollar and US treasuries at a time
OL,11,Fof economic and political uncertainty.
OL,13,FNo more - because he personally has
OL,14,Fbecome the world's source of economic
OL,15,Funcertainty and anxiety.
